頭仔</blockquote><br />\n呢樣唔比你嗰樣又話唔比，得返d 死貨垃圾貨叫你攞，仲要批到勁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔攞仲要單打你無單 單細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係講緊呢間，不過真係好多香港牌子係咁<br />\n而家百貨公司都無生意<br />\nd sales 日日比上邊卒數，上邊d 人又唔知自己仆街<br />\n以前意氣風發，而家見親都死老豆咁<br />\n心都涼埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}